S.FORM: Baldwin Lonsdale ryax sa tay nqu tay , Baldwin Lonsdale, squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay ) mrhuw Vanuatu ta' misuw hya' ga Baldwin Lonsdale, aring ryax tay 22 squ byacing tay 9 sa kawas 2014 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. qnxan nya(qyanux nya) kawas tay 1948,Baldwin Lonsdale htagan beh sa Banks Islands Mota Lava. kawas tay 2017,6 byacing 17 ryax.nbu wal mhuqil la maki Port Vila.(68 kawas)
